## Update Member Role

### Description
Updates the role of a member in an organization. This operation requires the user to have the necessary permissions.

### Method
POST

### Endpoint
/organization/update-member-role

### Parameters
#### Request Body
- **role** (string | string[]) - Required - The new role(s) to be applied to the member.
- **memberId** (string) - Required - The ID of the member whose role is to be updated.
- **organizationId** (string) - Optional - The ID of the organization. If not provided, session headers must be used to determine the active organization.

### Request Example
```json
{
  "role": ["admin", "sale"],
  "memberId": "member-id",
  "organizationId": "organization-id"
}
