### Update Member Role

Source: https://better-auth.com/docs/plugins/organization

Use `authClient.organization.updateMemberRole` to update a member's role. Ensure the user has the necessary permissions. The `organizationId` is optional if session headers are provided.

```javascript
await authClient.organization.updateMemberRole({
    role: ["admin", "sale"], // required
    memberId: "member-id", // required
    organizationId: "organization-id",
});
```

